    <note>Zhu(1) Mingzhi [526] Almost certainly Sun's [521] grandson. Wang(2) Yi(3)'s [7082] son-in-law, Wang(2) Anshi's [1762] and Wang(2) Anli's [1760] brother-in-law. His grandnephew, Zhu(1) Yanzhi [3266], first married the daughter of Shen(2) Li [1452] and when she died, he then married the daughter of Wang(2) Dingchen [3983], who has the same generational name as the brothers and cousins of Wang(2) Yaochen [1919]. XCB, 335.3a; SHY:ZG, 66.16a. CBD, 2, 609.</note>
